                <note rend="inline" type="source">823.001 Sanchez Cerro, Luis/54: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Peru</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dearing</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Lima</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1931-12-08T15:00:00-05:00"
                            >December 8, 1931—3 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received 4:36 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>381. Referring to my telegram No. 378, December 6, 10 a.m.,<note n="29"
                        xml:id="d1013fn29">Not printed.</note> inauguration of Sanchez Cerro took
                    place today about 1 o’clock in the Chamber of Deputies without untoward
                    incident.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dearing</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
